1\" src=\"/images/guitar/Melody_SpanishRomance-Part1.png\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 300px;\" /><img alt=\"melody2\" src=\"/images/guitar/Melody_SpanishRomance-Part2.png\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 300px;\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 class=\"accordion\">Prelude in C Major - Bach</h2>\n\n<div>\n<h5 class=\"accordion\">Scale</h5>\n\n<div>\n<p>C Major scale</p>\n</div>\n\n<h5 class=\"accordion\">Voice Leading</h5>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>CEGCE -&gt; CDADF -&gt; BDGDF -&gt; CEGCE -&gt; CEAEA -&gt; CDF#AD -&gt; BDGDG -&gt; BCEGC -&gt; ACEGC -&gt; F#ADAC or DADF#C -&gt; GBDGB -&gt; GBbEGC# -&gt; FADAD -&gt; FDFAbB or FAbDFB -&gt; EGCGC -&gt; EFACF -&gt; DFADF -&gt; GBGBF -&gt; CEGCE -&gt; CEBbCE -&gt; FFACE -&gt; F#CF#AEb -&gt; AbDFCD -&gt; GDBFBD -&gt; GEGCE -&gt; GDGCF -&gt; GDGBF -&gt; GEbACGb -&gt; GEGCG -&gt; GDGCF -&gt; GDGBF -&gt; CEBbCE -&gt; CCFAC (FCA) -&gt; CAFAF (DFD) -&gt; CDGBD (FDB) -&gt; DBGBD (FED) -&gt; CEGC</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#8e44ad;\"><strong><em>Mostly smooth transition of a note by step, Sometimes by half a step, And few times by leap</em></strong></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "authorId": 1, "subject": "hidden", "tags": [], "img": "", "summary": "", "lastUpdated": "2022-05-20 21:28:54.757111"}